blog.description:
librisognierealta.it è il mio blog.
Ho sempre sentito il bisogno di averne uno, ma non avevo mai trovato un argomento che mi spingesse a continuare a scrivere, finché non ho abbracciato la mia natura ossessia-compulsiva e assolutamente pignola! Da questo è nato il mio blog di recensioni e scleri di vario genere: Libri, Sogni e Realtà.

title: [Spoilers] Arya is Arya
body:
It seems as if many still believe Arya could be the waiff wearing her face for some reason. When Arya sees Nymeria it’s pretty clear that Arya is in fact Arya, even if she told her the direwolfs name. The scene would make no sense, the sense of smell a direwolfs must have is evidence enough.

Little finger is dead. I’ve seen theories where some are saying he could be a faceless man but it just isn’t so. I know he’s a popular character and many hate the way he died but with Brandon Stark in the picture it’s not likely. I’d say I’m 99% sure Arya is Arya and Little Finger is dead if not the three eyed raven would have said so.



Source: https://ift.tt/2DRac9v

summary: In an odd adventure such as Emma has never known, her new friends from Westeros are expelled from their world, just as Emma is...
body: In an odd adventure such as Emma has never known, her new friends from Westeros are expelled from their world, just as Emma is from Storybrooke with Hook. First the Starks and some of Daenyers’ company end up in Storybrooke, for a long enough period they start to wear the world’s kind of clothing to blend in. Unfortunately Emma and her friends end up in Claire and Jamie’s world then, unable to figure out how to get back to their own worlds.
